  "content_id": "6b905674-a660-4b16-9435-63282efefc4c",
  "description": "Financial help with sending your child to a specialist school for young musicians and dancers",
  "details": {
    "body": "<p>You could get help to pay for your child to go to a specialist music or dance school.</p>\n\n<p>The Music and Dance Scheme provides grants and help with fees at 8 schools and 20 Centres for Advanced Training (<abbr title=\"Centres for Advanced Training\">CATs</abbr>).</p>\n\n<p>You can apply for help to pay for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>full time study at a school</li>\n  <li>part time study at a <abbr title=\"Centre for Advanced Training\">CAT</abbr>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"age-eligibility\">Age eligibility</h2>\n\n<p>To be eligible, your child must be aged:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>8 to 19 for music schools or <abbr title=\"Centres for Advanced Training\">CATs</abbr>\n</li>\n  <li>11 to 19 for dance schools or <abbr title=\"Centres for Advanced Training\">CATs</abbr>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Disabled students at music and dance <abbr title=\"Centres for Advanced Training\">CATs</abbr> are eligible up to the age of 25.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Music and dance CATs will not usually accept new applications from students who’ll be 17 or over when they start.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply\">How to apply</h2>\n\n<p>Apply directly to the school or <abbr title=\"Centre for Advanced Training\">CAT</abbr>.</p>\n\n<p>You’ll usually need to fill out a form and your child will need to audition.</p>\n\n<p>The school or <abbr title=\"Centre for Advanced Training\">CAT</abbr> will ask for information about your household income to decide how much funding your child can get.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"music-and-dance-schools\">Music and dance schools</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"music-schools\">Music schools</h3>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"col\">Name</th>\n      <th scope=\"col\">Location</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://chethamsschoolofmusic.com/admissions/fees-and-finance/\">Chetham’s School of Music</a></td>\n      <td>Manchester</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.purcell-school.org/admissions/fees/\">The Purcell School</a></td>\n      <td>Hertfordshire</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://wells.cathedral.school/specialist-music-scholarships/\">Wells Cathedral School</a></td>\n      <td>Somerset</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.menuhinschool.co.uk/school/admissions/Music-Dance-Scheme\">The Yehudi Menuhin School</a></td>\n      <td>Surrey</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3 id=\"dance-schools\">Dance schools</h3>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"col\">Name</th>\n      <th scope=\"col\">Location</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://elmhurstballetschool.org/en/apply/funding-and-fees-calculator/\">Elmhurst Ballet School</a></td>\n      <td>Birmingham</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.thehammond.co.uk/fees-funding\">The Hammond School</a></td>\n      <td>Chester</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.royalballetschool.org.uk/information/fees/full-time-training-fees/\">Royal Ballet School</a></td>\n      <td>London</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.tringpark.com/fees-funding/\">Tring Park School</a></td>\n      <td>Hertfordshire</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"music-and-dance-cats\">Music and dance <abbr title=\"Centres for Advanced Training\">CATs</abbr>\n</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"music-cats\">Music <abbr title=\"Centres for Advanced Training\">CATs</abbr>\n</h3>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"col\">Name</th>\n      <th scope=\"col\">Location</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://brittenpearsarts.org/take-part/artists/aldeburgh-young-musicians/the-aym-programme\">Aldeburgh Young Musicians</a></td>\n      <td>Suffolk</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.gsmd.ac.uk/study-with-guildhall/children-and-young-people/guildhall-young-artists/centre-for-young-musicians\">Centre for Young Musicians</a></td>\n      <td>London</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.gsmd.ac.uk/study-with-guildhall/children-and-young-people/guildhall-young-artists/junior-guildhall/finance-and-funding\">Guildhall School of Music &amp; Drama</a></td>\n      <td>London</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.ram.ac.uk/study/departments/junior-academy/fees-financial-support\">Royal Academy of Music</a></td>\n      <td>London</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.bcu.ac.uk/conservatoire/music/juniors/how-to-apply/fees-financial-support\">Royal Birmingham Conservatoire</a></td>\n      <td>Birmingham</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.rcm.ac.uk/junior/rcmjdapply/rcmjdfeesandfunding/\">Royal College of Music</a></td>\n      <td>London</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.rncm.ac.uk/study-here/junior-rncm/\">Royal Northern College of Music</a></td>\n      <td>Manchester</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.sheffieldmusicacademy.org/\">Sheffield Music Academy</a></td>\n      <td>Sheffield</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.swms.org.uk/about/\">South West Music School</a></td>\n      <td>South West England</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://theglasshouseicm.org/make-music/young-people/bursaries/\">The Glasshouse</a></td>\n      <td>Gateshead</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.trinitylaban.ac.uk/study/music/junior-trinity/term-dates-fees\">Trinity Laban Conservatoire of Music and Dance</a></td>\n      <td>London</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://yorkshireyoungmusicians.uk/money-matters-fees-support/\">Yorkshire Young Musicians</a></td>\n      <td>Leeds, Hull</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3 id=\"dance-cats\">Dance <abbr title=\"Centres for Advanced Training\">CATs</abbr>\n</h3>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"col\">Name</th>\n      <th scope=\"col\">Location</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.dancecity.co.uk/training-academy/cat-centre-for-advanced-training/\">Dance City</a></td>\n      <td>Newcastle upon Tyne</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.danceeast.co.uk/costs-and-funding/\">Dance East</a></td>\n      <td>Suffolk</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://fabric.dance/centre-for-advanced-training/\">FABRIC (East Midlands)</a></td>\n      <td>Nottingham</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://fabric.dance/yuva-gati/\">FABRIC (South Asian National Strand)</a></td>\n      <td>Birmingham, across the UK</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://fabric.dance/centre-for-advanced-training/\">FABRIC (West Midlands)</a></td>\n      <td>Birmingham</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://thelowry.com/get-creative/young-people/dance\">The Lowry</a></td>\n      <td>Salford</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nationalcircus.org.uk/youth/centre-for-advanced-training\">National Centre for Circus Arts</a></td>\n      <td>London, across the UK</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://northernballet.com/academy/professional-training/centre-for-advanced-training\">Northern Ballet</a></td>\n      <td>Leeds</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nscd.ac.uk/take-part/cat/\">Northern School of Contemporary Dance</a></td>\n      <td>Leeds</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://theplace.org.uk/dance/centre-for-advanced-training\">The Place</a> </td>\n      <td>London</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.swindondance.org.uk/cat/funded-dance-training/\">Swindon Dance</a></td>\n      <td>Swindon</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.trinitylaban.ac.uk/course/centre-for-advanced-training/\">Trinity Laban Conservatoire of Music and Dance</a></td>\n      <td>London</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"choir-schools-scholarship-scheme\">Choir Schools Scholarship Scheme</h2>\n\n<p>If your child is aged 8 to 13, you could get financial help with sending them to an independent cathedral or collegiate choir school. Contact the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.choirschools.org.uk/help-with-fees/\">Choir Schools’ Association</a> directly to apply.</p>\n\n",
